<body>
	<div class="easyui-panel" style="width:600px;height:500px;padding:20px"
		title="문제1" data-options="footer:'#footer'">
		<form id="f_test1" method="get" action="test2.jsp">
		<input type="hidden" id="dap1" name="dap1"/>
		DML구문 중에서 성격이 다른 하나를 고르시오.
		<div style="margin-bottom=20px"></div>
		<br>
		<input class="easyui-checkbox" name="cb" value="Orange" onChange="answer(0)">
		1.INSERT
		<div style="margin-bottom=20px"></div>
		<br>
		<input class="easyui-checkbox" name="cb" value="Orange" onChange="answer(1)">
		2.SELECT
		<div style="margin-bottom=20px"></div>
		<br>
	    <input class="easyui-checkbox" name="cb" value="Orange" onChange="answer(2)">
	    3.UPDATE
	    <div style="margin-bottom=20px"></div>
	    <br>
		<input class="easyui-checkbox" name="cb" value="Orange" onChange="answer(3)">
		4.DELETE
		<div style="margin-bottom=20px" ></div>
		</form>
